# Motion Personality (überagent)

Read `design/design.md` and use presets from `website/src/motion/`.

## Style

calm · elegant · precise · premium · technical · restrained · system-like · fast but not nervous · cinematic only in hero/scroll sections

## Avoid

bouncy springs · excessive parallax · particle chaos · scroll-jacking · long delays · overanimated SaaS sections · animating every element

## Rules

- Import from `motion/react`, presets from `../motion`
- Use `useReducedMotion()` for entrance animations
- Animate only `opacity` and `transform` (x, y, scale)
- Springs: `stiffness: 420, damping: 38` – no bounce
- Durations: 0.2–0.55s (hero max 0.75s)
- Stagger: 50–60ms between children
- Modals: `AnimatePresence` + `modalOverlay` / `modalDialog` presets
- Cards: subtle `y: -2` hover, `scale: 0.99` tap only
